![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/64769428-4251-4eb1-808b-c29cf1236eb5/e303.jpg)

Halloween has come and gone but there's still some spookiness in the air, as the guy at CBC parse through one of the darker stories in DC Comics history, Blackest Night! Join us as we talk about the Green Lantern Corps, debate the usefulness of character resurrections, and do our best to summarize this EPIC tale about death, life, and what makes it all worthwhile.  

Please leave us a **_review_** on [**ITunes**](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us wherever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our merchandise! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by **ComicBook Clique**, the only stop for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.  

